<chapter id="introduction">
 <title>Introduction</title>
  <para>&kfilereplace; is an application used to perform searching and replacing of a list of strings in a file tree. The strings may be literals or QT-like regular expressions. There are even other options that you may use to tune your search.
  </para>
</chapter>

